item.title: By: Shweta
item.dc:creator: Shweta
item.description: not worth it to mine solo on btc plus, but if you have a decent nubemr of visitors it adds up. I've only generated enough for 1 payout of .02 btc, and much of that was from me going to all the demo computers when i was shopping one day and going to my link.
